hostname.name: hostname
hostname.queryValue: select distinct JSONExtractString(labels, 'host_name') from signoz_metrics.distributed_time_series_v2 where metric_name ILIKE 'jvm_%' and JSONExtractString(labels, 'service_name')={{.serviceName}};

serviceName.name: serviceName
serviceName.queryValue: select distinct JSONExtractString(labels, 'service_name') from signoz_metrics.distributed_time_series_v2 where metric_name ILIKE 'jvm_%';
